title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Help Out with Dispatch Work
content:
Bombs, drugs, and kingpins will keep you busy in newly available Dispatch Work. Clean up the streets of Los Santos and you’ll be rewarded generously with GTA$ and RP for your efforts.

Get your hands on your own law enforcement vehicle from Warstock Cache & Carry and you’ll be able to launch Dispatch Work while inside.
